# Basic

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:bpf, path: ".."}
])
```

## Opening & Loading

```elixir
object = BPF.Object.open_file!("syscall_counter.o")
```

```elixir
BPF.Object.load!(object)
```

```elixir
[_, map] = object.maps
```

```elixir
BPF.Map.lookup_elem!(map, 0)
```

```elixir
BPF.Map.update_elem!(map, 0, %{"t1" => 0x4200420042004200, "t2" => 123.456})
```

```elixir
BPF.Map.lookup_elem!(map, 0)
```
